    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for anyone needing dependable daily transportation. While the engine and transmission are in good working order and the car drives well, it does show its age through various cosmetic imperfections. You can expect some noticeable scratches and minor dings on the exterior, along with typical wear and tear on the interior upholstery and plastic trim. It is a solid, functional vehicle that has been maintained mechanically but lacks the aesthetic polish of a newer model.",
